      <title>巴西钢铁行业因国家减排目标而“惊恐不已”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/brazil-steel-sector-pushes-back-on-country-s-carbon-emissions-targets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[行业组织Aco Brasil的负责人表示，巴西在阿塞拜疆举行的联合国气候变化大会上宣布的雄心勃勃的减排目标“吓坏”了这个南美国家的钢铁公司，它们拒绝采取无法实现的目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/brazil-steel-sector-pushes-back-on-country-s-carbon-emissions-targets</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Dec 2024 22:15:03 GMT</pubDate>
