      <title>加拿大财政部长辞职 赤字进一步扩大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/canada-runs-deeper-deficits-as-finance-chief-resigns</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大总理贾斯汀·特鲁多领导的政府赤字超出预期，并打破了财政部长制定的财政目标。财政部长在即将公布新的支出和收入预估的当天辞职。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/canada-runs-deeper-deficits-as-finance-chief-resigns</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Dec 2024 21:15:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特鲁多任命勒布朗为加拿大财政部长 政府陷入混乱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/trudeau-to-name-leblanc-canada-finance-minister-with-government-in-chaos</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大总理贾斯汀·特鲁多任命多米尼克·勒布朗为加拿大财政部长，接替克里斯蒂亚·弗里兰。弗里兰的辞职信措辞严厉，令人震惊，信中暗示政府对唐纳德·特朗普回归的准备工作做得不周。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/trudeau-to-name-leblanc-canada-finance-minister-with-government-in-chaos</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Dec 2024 20:29:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>比特币创下 2021 年以来最长周涨幅纪录</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-15/bitcoin-btc-hits-record-after-longest-weekly-winning-run-since-2021</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于当选总统唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 对数字资产的支持，以及对即将将持有该代币的 MicroStrategy Inc. 纳入美国关键股票指数的乐观态度，比特币价格创下历史新高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-15/bitcoin-btc-hits-record-after-longest-weekly-winning-run-since-2021</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 15 Dec 2024 23:49:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
